SUMMARY:Northside Hospital Peachtree Road Race
LOCATION:Atlanta\, GA
DESCRIPTION:The world's largest 10K road race. Ham radio operators provide 
 communications support for the medical branch. Positions include Water Stop
 s\, pace cars\, shadows\, start and finish line assignments\, and Call Take
 rs in the Multi-Agency Coordination Center (MACC). You do not need to be an
  ARES member to participate. Call Taker positions do not require an Amateur
  Radio license.
URL:https://atlantatrackclub.volunteerlocal.com/volunteer/?id=110344
CATEGORIES:Public Service
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
