SUMMARY:Peachy Trunkfest & Swap
LOCATION:Fayetteville\, GA
DESCRIPTION:A casual\, vehicle-based tailgate swap meet hosted by the Fayet
 te County Amateur Radio Club (KK4GQ). Buy\, sell\, and trade used amateur r
 adio equipment — rigs\, antennas\, parts — directly from your trunk. FR
 EE to attend and sell! Complimentary coffee and donuts while supplies last.
  Cash is highly recommended. Sellers should arrive 8:00am–8:45am. Talk-In
 : 145.210 (–) PL 131.8 Hz. Vehicle-based event only — no tents\, extern
 al tables\, amplified sound\, alcohol\, or open fires.
URL:https://kk4gq.org/peachy
CATEGORIES:Meeting
STATUS:CONFIRMED
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
END:VEVENT
