LOCATION:Hebron Baptist Church\, 202 Hebron Church Rd\, Dacula\, GA 30019
DESCRIPTION:Ham radio operators help coordinate the Dacula Memorial Day Par
 ade by lining up participants (vehicles\, floats\, marching bands\, groups\
 , tractors\, and horses) at Hebron Baptist Church so they depart in the cor
 rect order for announcement at the Announcing Stand.
